{"type": "article", "id": 17644, "title": "磁性笔记本", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-17T06:50:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 124, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135523YtWe0xaDrg84IKqf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个看似平淡的笔记本里有种特殊的磁性吸附的功能。每一页的边缘都带有磁性，可以随意插入取出以调整顺序，比线圈本更加快速方便。笔记本和其中的纸张都能固定在带磁性的白板或者冰箱上，成为便利贴。它本身也能正常放在打印机里打印，与电子产品一起使用。这个本子一共有 120 页和 4 种格式，外面是黑色的人造皮革，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/273274561/rekonect-notebook-the-magnetic-lifestyle#\" target=\"_blank\">目前正在众筹。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144728d5YRGZ4LzM8NxwIr.gif\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261447338fiB4WdyPuHMYsGm.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144734OoMPAxB76hUkwTRr.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144735bZ8kOLrme397wquv.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144735S0brCnEqlkvQ4oIi.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}